Text: RE Toll Tag Stacey Bring your transponder back to the parking and transpotation office located on the third floor ECN Once we have your transponder we will activate your EZ tag Original Message From White Stacey W Sent Tuesday October PM To Katz Martin Subject Toll Tag Martin I have both a toll tag and a parking transponder My toll tag is Please let me know what else I need to do Thanks Stacey White
